Create Project

To create a project:

  1. Select the Create button
  2. Select the context you want the project to be created
     

    Note: You can create the Project in the context of a cultural object or in the context of another Project or any system object. Creating Project in the context of another system objects means that this Project will be part of that context and the permissions on that Project will depend on this context.

     

  3. Select "Project" from the drop-down with types.
     

    Note: To find easily the Project in the list with system objects that can be created you can start to type directly in the field. The list with types is filtered as you write in the field.

     

  4. Fill Project Details section fields

    Note: Only required fields are displayed in create dialog. I f you want to filled in additional properties you could select 'See more' option that should show all properties of the project, which are not explicitly displayed in create dialog.

     

  5. Press Create
